 have brought this action against Donald H. Rumsfeld, in his official capacity as the United States Secretary of Defense (\u8220\'3fDoD\u8221\'3f or the \u8220\'3fGovernment\u8221\'3f). This action arises out of DoD\rquote s application of the Solomon Amendment against Yale University as a result of a YLS non-discrimination policy.
